creator: ConnectPay
descriptionHtml:
ConnectPay mobile application offers multi-factor authentication at the convenience of your mobile device.
Use your fingerprint, Face ID or PIN to easily add an additional layer of security to protect your account from shady interests of others.

How to register your device:
- Login to your ConnectPay Online Banking account
- If you don’t have any registered devices yet – you will be offered to register one
- Click “REGISTER” button to proceed and you will receive the QR code
- Open your ConnectPay App and scan the QR code presented on the website
- Once the QR code is successfully scanned, please proceed with the next steps on your app to complete registration

Easy banking features on the App:
- Register your device via QR code
- Secure your account using biometrics or PIN
- Get notifications for one-tap approval (login, payments and more)

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- Fingerprint scanner issues has been addressed
- Small UI improvements
- App stability improvements
- App update functionality implemented

title: ConnectPay

creator: ConnectPay
descriptionHtml:
Welcome to ConnectPay mobile application – your ultimate financial wingman! Whether you need to pay bills or transfer money, our app makes it a breeze with quick and secure payment options, all at the touch of a button. Keep track of your cards list and manage them like a pro. Plus, with multi-factor authentication, you can connect to your online banking without any fuss and be sure your transactions are secure.

With ConnectPay, managing your money is simple and effortless – so go ahead, relax, and let us take care of your finances!

Easy banking features:
• Secure your account using biometrics or PIN
• Get notifications for one-tap approval (login, payments, and more)
• Seamlessly access your Online Banking by logging in to your app
